snippet.title: Release Trailer | Kebab Chefs! - Restaurant Simulator
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1001270
Join our discord community! https://discord.gg/ceY3MyS

Twitter: https://twitter.com/KebabChefs
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/kebabchefs
Website: https://biotechgameworks.com/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/studiobiotech

Kebab Chefs! is a Co-Op, cooking and restaurant management game that can be played up to 4 players. Design your own restaurant. Cook delicious foods, fill your menu with various recipes, feed customers and become the biggest kebab restaurant in town!
